numRow = '1000'

def url_req(keyid,StartDate,EndDate):
    url_data1 = 'http://api.visitkorea.or.kr/openapi/service/rest/KorService/searchFestival?serviceKey='+keyid
    url_data2 = '&MobileOS=ETC&MobileApp=AppTest&arrange=A&numOfRows='+numRow+'&pageNo=1&listYN=Y'
    url_data3 = url_data2+'&eventStartDate='+StartDate+'&eventEndDate='+EndDate
    url_result = url_data1 + url_data3
    return url_result

import datetime
import numpy as np


prn_item = []

for temp in data:
    
    try:
        Title = temp.find('title').text
        Add = temp.find('addr1').text
        Sdate = temp.find('eventstartdate').text  # 20191130
        Sdate = Sdate[0:4]+'-'+Sdate[4:6]+'-'+Sdate[-2:]   #2019-11-30
        Sdate = datetime.datetime.strptime(Sdate,'%Y-%m-%d')
        Edate = temp.find('eventenddate').text  # 20191130
        Edate = Edate[0:4]+'-'+Edate[4:6]+'-'+Edate[-2:]   #2019-11-30
        Edate = datetime.datetime.strptime(Edate,'%Y-%m-%d')

        if temp.find('mapy'):
            mapY = temp.find('mapy').text
            mapX = temp.find('mapx').text
        else :
            mapY = np.nan
            mapX = np.nan


        Tel = temp.find('tel').text

        pdata = {'축제명' : Title , '주소' : Add, '연락처' : Tel , '시작일':Sdate ,
                '종료일':Edate , '위도':mapY, '경도':mapX}

        prn_item.append(pdata)
        
    except:
        
        print('오류가 있는 데이터')
        Title = temp.find('title').text
        print(Title)
    
    
   
df = pd.DataFrame(prn_item)
